### **Combat & Piece Hierarchy**

*(Attacker -> Defender : Result)*
- **Lure -> Snare:** Lure Wins
- **Snare -> Hook:** Snare Wins
- **Hook -> Lure:** Hook Wins
- **Bait -> Snare:** Bait Wins
- **Hook -> Bait:** Bait Wins
- **Lure -> Bait:** Bait Wins and Defender take back instant lost coins
- **Lure -> Lure:** Attacker Wins and Defender take back instant lost coins
- **Snare -> Snare:** Defender Wins
- **Hook -> Hook:** Attacker Wins

